Operation Tannenbaum [PL 2.0]

 - hypothetic scenario -

The OKW decided to attack the neutral Switzerland. It is supported by retreating french units. The germans attacked with 12 divisions. The defense contains of 5 infantry divisions, 3 regiments mountaineers, 4 artillery regiments and the whole fortress line.

This fictive scenario is about the first attacking wave of the Germans and their italian allies.

